<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>枯藤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月匆匆叹不禁，风霜尽染老残身。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嶙峋瘦骨无须笑，莫忘当年那绿荫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200906/02c00aba715e4890baf67d5322b47dcf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
