<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老树</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经年历久已形衰，心里阳光不自哀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嬉戏孩童偏爱我，一番拥抱一番猜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200906/283b62227ca240cc9f75120e7abc3957.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>昏鸦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽叫昏鸦鸦未昏，尚知何处可栖身。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只缘那日归巢晚，写入诗行吟到今。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200906/d7213b5ca47f40138974994b0ec3b506.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小桥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此生乐与水为邻，也净心来也净魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一卧微躯行义举，成全世上有情人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200906/f39a11b158b447c8b6d8b42f92af05ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别离故土与家山，再好风光岂可贪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百转千回能不腐，以身示范话为官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200906/72fa5897a8084dda81f9bcce09e89d12.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远在山中世代居，薄田开垦两三畦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主人新酿那壶酒，尽是汗滴与泪滴。</p>
